snippet.title: Zack Peter
snippet.description: Zack Peter is a pop-culture and wellness junkie turned published author, podcaster, and unsolicited advice-giver. As a writer, he’s published a total of four books, with work featured on POPSUGAR, Men’s Health, Yahoo and more. You can catch his signature wit and gift of gab as host of #NoFilter with Zack Peter (a juicy podcast for pop-culture and reality TV lovers) and #ADULTING (a lifestyle podcast for millennial go-getters living life on their own terms). Keep up (if you can) at @justplainzack
